{"tid":1478204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大家點睇出路","createTime":"2019-08-16T11:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T03:54:21.000Z","uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6986dd30bab295e3bb7a290b34d5e7a5027db3","tid":1478204,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"提一提,請你睇完先屌<br />\n<br />\n1. 大家有冇睇個無間道? <br />\n我見大家好似O 記出鬼+砌生豬肉 好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. 其實你見o記係前線你就明啦!<br />\n   佢地不嬲都係做呢D<br />\n<br />\n好多時我見大家黑衫頭盔出街  真係好能洋,你唔怕便衣? 我林O記實有你地D 料.<br />\n成12點返屋企會落單架? 唔搵多幾個朋友接? D黑警黑社會實找上你.你估你係李小龍<br />\n睇完先屌<br />\n<br />\n2.  share 下啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6z6mqT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6z6mqT.jpg&h=2848c4ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好鍾意睇'71 . (71暴亂夜) , 講北愛共和軍與英國暴亂. 其實依家好似香港<br />\n佢可能幫到勇武, 文宣,和理非林下依家可以點做先好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 知己知彼 百戰百勝<br />\n大陸唔出公安好內, 共產黨係出國安, 特警,黑社會, 潮陽大媽.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-46919009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-46919009&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=69274b73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-46919009&h=f3eb08d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-46919009</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20181220/xinjiang-uighur-homes/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fopinion%2F20181220%2Fxinjiang-uighur-homes%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=3996411e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20181220/xinjiang-uighur-homes/zh-hant/</a><br />\n你捉唔灑鬼的.除非你捉灑所有共產黨黨員<br />\n你只能做好自己,813罷明用愛字頭挑起你地情緒...中計啦...前線真係要拉一拉住D手捉,唔係只用口....建議係件衫上寫冷靜d互相提醒<br />\n<br />\n4.大家要睇下人民日報(一路睇一路屌), 因為阿爺似終有解放軍. 你無可能打得過<br />\n要知所進退,到時唔係送頭係送葬<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/布拉格之春\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E5%B8%83%E6%8B%89%E6%A0%BC%E4%B9%8B%E6%98%A5&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=f50b424a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/布拉格之春</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 林下有冇可能818 有300 萬人上街仲好<br />\n<br />\n6. 支爆<br />\n    有冇睇過V煞? <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtnPAxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtnPAxJ.jpg&h=4a9a463c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n   中國人似乎都有D腦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/2001%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98/3415410?fromtitle=%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98&amp;fromid=6792239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F2001%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%2598%2F3415410%3Ffromtitle%3D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%2598%26fromid%3D6792239&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=669089b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/2001%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98/3415410?fromtitle=%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%98&amp;fromid=6792239</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">死都不割蓆</span></strong><br />\n818一定支持 但唔好送頭啊"},{"pid":"cf6bc200f82b3fa9cf33bbbd7755c11a67a20ffa","tid":1478204,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6986dd30bab295e3bb7a290b34d5e7a5027db3","tid":1478204,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"提一提,請你睇完先屌<br />\n<br />\n1. 大家有冇睇個無間道? <br />\n我見大家好似O 記出鬼+砌生豬肉 好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a